    <entry>
      <title>往期美食</title>
      <link href="/archives/2022/04/04/%E5%BE%80%E6%9C%9F%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F/"/>
      <url>/archives/2022/04/04/%E5%BE%80%E6%9C%9F%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211156664.png" alt="image-20220404211156664"></p><p>疫情前一个月，这个时候体重就已经刹不住车了，，，</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211258083.png" alt="image-20220404211258083"></p><span id="more"></span><p>买的小米电炒锅，试试</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211424917.png" alt="image-20220404211424917"></p><p>芹菜炒肉</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211501554.png" alt="image-20220404211501554"></p><p>md智障，当时还以为大学有多轻松、诗意</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211548027.png" alt="image-20220404211548027"></p><p>香蕉奶昔？记不太清了，好像就是酸奶块配纯牛奶，再煎x个蛋</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211700858.png" alt="image-20220404211700858"></p><p>新买的不粘锅，练习煎蛋（这个时候我的锅还不黑~）</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211747931.png" alt="image-20220404211747931"></p><p>魔芋粉丝，健康起来了</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211829174.png" alt="image-20220404211829174"></p><p>杰哥杰嫂的，看起来不错，还在逸都国际这个时候，20年5月份</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404211950152.png" alt="image-20220404211950152"></p><p>这个很确定就是，香蕉奶昔</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212036887.png" alt="image-20220404212036887"></p><p>逸都国际1202号</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212115816.png" alt="image-20220404212115816"></p><p>疫情来了，食堂自取餐，很拉胯</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212204623.png" alt="image-20220404212204623"></p><p>还是逸都国际1202</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212252553.png" alt="image-20220404212252553"></p><p>出发去青城山，hiahia</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212330797.png" alt="image-20220404212330797"></p><p>爷爷的爱情来啦~</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212419481.png" alt="img"></p><p>20200913面目全非……</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212719016.png" alt="image-20220404212719016"></p><p>20200914结束了……</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212610204.png" alt="image-20220404212610204"></p><p>假精致</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212650200.png" alt="image-20220404212650200"></p><p>清凉一夏</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404212905523.png" alt="image-20220404212905523"></p><p>垃圾投产餐</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404213135293.png" alt="image-20220404213135293"></p><p>减肥魔芋方便面</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404213342825.png" alt="image-20220404213342825"></p><p>21年过年前</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404213834010.png" alt="image-20220404213834010"></p><p>红烧排骨</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404213906598.png" alt="image-20220404213906598"></p><p>整个全套的</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214009380.png" alt="image-20220404214009380"></p><p>想回去，被拒绝，遇一小女孩，对我笑，哈哈</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214125101.png" alt="image-20220404214125101"></p><p>家公家婆 2021.02.11 15:45:37</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214204948.png" alt="image-20220404214204948"></p><p>20200217 和戳哥小聚，鸭脑壳飞</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214330009.png" alt="image-20220404214330009"></p><p>自作聪明</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cheng000/picture/main/image-20220404214406571.png" alt="image-20220404214406571"></p><p>20210228 戳哥、杰哥 郫都区 海底捞，戳哥肉眼可见的肥了</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214450754.png" alt="image-20220404214450754"></p><p>自制凉面</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214633303.png" alt="image-20220404214633303"></p><p>21年公司开春</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214707572.png" alt="image-20220404214707572"></p><p>角落的小野菊</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214744736.png" alt="image-20220404214744736"></p><p>搬家了，美城悦荣府，20210320</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214833746.png" alt="image-20220404214833746"></p><p>练手</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214915934.png" alt="image-20220404214915934"></p><p>朦胧派</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404214948572.png" alt="image-20220404214948572"></p><p>芒果奶昔，这次水平见长</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215023661.png" alt="image-20220404215023661"></p><p>20210501 乐山 美食街 张公桥</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215120004.png" alt="image-20220404215120004"></p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215159958.png" alt="image-20220404215159958" style="zoom:25%;" /><p>20210509 自制小烧烤</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215241736.png" alt="image-20220404215241736"></p><p>角落</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215434968.png" alt="image-20220404215434968"></p><p>出发</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215506235.png" alt="image-20220404215506235"></p><p>20210619 这次投产餐还阔以，没忍住多拿了</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215555933.png" alt="image-20220404215555933"></p><p>20210830 算法竞赛摆拍</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215645580.png" alt="image-20220404215645580"></p><p>老八咖喱牛右</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215732449.png" alt="image-20220404215732449"></p><p>20211003 国庆去重庆耍</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215817541.png" alt="image-20220404215817541"></p><p>忘了这个叫啥子火锅了，一般般，重庆美食感觉还不如成都</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215902484.png" alt="image-20220404215902484"></p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215931628.png" alt="image-20220404215931628"></p><p>返程</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404215951210.png" alt="image-20220404215951210"></p><p>秘制肉丸粉丝</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220021543.png" alt="image-20220404220021543"></p><p>自制烤香肠</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220048172.png" alt="image-20220404220048172"></p><p>20211114 煎鳕鱼片</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220157265.png" alt="image-20220404220157265"></p><p>减肥 小 鸡腿</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220225197.png" alt="image-20220404220225197"></p><p>映秀爬山10多公里，晚上公司安排聚餐，饿安逸了</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220311417.png" alt="image-20220404220311417"></p><p>20220130 过年咯</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220357936.png" alt="image-20220404220357936"></p><p>我大孝泉</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220442384.png" alt="image-20220404220442384"></p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220508168.png" alt="image-20220404220508168"></p><p>老家一起吃柴火鸡，绵竹年画村</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/78445B29-731D-4355-8AA7-52D1DDB1AA6B_1_105_c.jpeg" alt="78445B29-731D-4355-8AA7-52D1DDB1AA6B_1_105_c"></p><p>20220208年后返成都，与杰哥聚</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220708394.png" alt="image-20220404220708394"></p><p>20220313 减肥新征程</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220815927.png" alt="image-20220404220815927"></p><p>20220403 减肥有我，有我必胜</p><p><img src="https://ameng000.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/pic/image-20220404220903348.png" alt="image-20220404220903348"></p>]]></content>
      
      
